01:02:33.500 --> 01:02:37.294
♪ And his feet planted
firm on the ground ♪

01:02:37.295 --> 01:02:41.632
♪ And you won't see
nobody dare to try ♪

01:02:41.633 --> 01:02:44.760
♪ To boss him or toss him around! ♪

01:02:44.761 --> 01:02:48.681
♪ No fat bottomed, flabby
