Is a girl?

01:04:00.837 --> 01:04:03.756
Aw, Bill.

01:04:05.091 --> 01:04:06.759
Bill.

01:04:08.386 --> 01:04:10.763
What would I do with her?

01:04:10.764 --> 01:04:12.932
